data.description: Beautiful hard to find 4-bedroom, 3-full bathroom home in SE Visalia! This home built by Woodside homes is located across Majestic Park with RV/boat parking, this is the one you've been looking for! Bright and spacious, this home was designed with families in mind. The kitchen is highlighted with gorgeous granite counter tops, ample cabinetry and storage, large pantry and a center island with a breakfast bar. Plenty of room to host those special meals and for everyday dining. The incredible kitchen is also open to the spacious living room providing a seamless flow for easy living and entertaining. The living room is prewired for surround sound speakers for those movie nights. One bedroom and full bath are conveniently located on the main floor. Upstairs, you'll find 3 additional bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Superior owner's suite featuring a luxurious bath with dual sinks, an elegant jet spa soaking tub, and a large walk-in closet. Wonderful backyard with lots of potential offering a covered patio and shed included. Schedule your private showing today!
